7.30	Bernice_Bobs_Her_Hair	Bernice Bobs Her Hair	Bernice Bobs Her Hair is a short story by F. Scott Fitzgerald, written in 1920 and first published in the Saturday Evening Post in May of that year. It appeared shortly thereafter in the collection Flappers and Philosophers.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b2/Fitzgerald%2C_Saturday_evening_post.png/220px-Fitzgerald%2C_Saturday_evening_post.png
